# Types of Classification

## Binary Classification

Only two classes.

Examples:

* Spam / Not Spam
* Pass / Fail
* Fraud / Genuine

---

## Multi-Class Classification

More than two classes.

Examples:

* Digit Recognition (0–9)
* Animal Classification
* Language Identification

